# Docker build context (HF Spaces: Dockerfile COPY . .).
# Align with `.hfignore` for Hub upload; Docker supports `!` negation — use it only here
# when needed. Keep `openenv push` excludes free of `!` (see `.hfignore` header).

.git
.github

__pycache__
**/__pycache__
*.py[cod]
*$py.class
